#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "2. Lay Followers"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Mānatthaddhasutta"
msgstr "15. Stuck-Up"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.178"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.382"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena mānatthaddho nāma brāhmaṇo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati."
msgstr "Now at that time a brahmin named Stuck-Up was residing in Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.3"
msgid ""
"So neva mātaraṃ abhivādeti, na pitaraṃ abhivādeti, na ācariyaṃ abhivādeti, "
"na jeṭṭhabhātaraṃ abhivādeti."
msgstr ""
"He didn’t bow to his mother or father, his teacher, or his oldest brother."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.4"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā mahatiyā parisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time the Buddha was teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large "
"assembly."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.5"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddhassa brāhmaṇassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up thought:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.6"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo mahatiyā parisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti."
msgstr "“The ascetic Gotama is teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.7"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ."
msgstr "Why don’t I approach him?"

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.8"
msgid "Sace maṃ samaṇo gotamo ālapissati, ahampi taṃ ālapissāmi."
msgstr "If he speaks to me, I’ll speak to him."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.9"
msgid "No ce maṃ samaṇo gotamo ālapissati, ahampi nālapissāmī”ti."
msgstr "But if he doesn’t speak, neither will I.”"

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.10"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"tuṇhībhūto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Stuck-Up went up to the Buddha, and stood silently to one "
"side."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.11"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā taṃ nālapi."
msgstr "But the Buddha didn’t speak to him."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.12"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo:"
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up thought:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.13"
msgid "“nāyaṃ samaṇo gotamo kiñci jānātī”ti tatova puna nivattitukāmo ahosi."
msgstr ""
"“This ascetic Gotama knows nothing!” And he wanted to go back from there "
"right away."

msgctxt "sn7.15:1.14"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā mānatthaddhassa brāhmaṇassa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya "
"mānatthaddhaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, knowing what Stuck-Up was thinking, addressed him in verse:"

# See BB for reading.
#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.1"
msgid "“Na mānaṃ brāhmaṇa sādhu,"
msgstr "“It’s not good to foster conceit"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.2"
msgid "atthikassīdha brāhmaṇa;"
msgstr "if you want what’s good for you, brahmin."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.3"
msgid "Yena atthena āgacchi,"
msgstr "You should foster the goal"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:2.4"
msgid "tamevamanubrūhaye”ti."
msgstr "which brought you here.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.383"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo:"
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up thought:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.2"
msgid ""
"“cittaṃ me samaṇo gotamo jānātī”ti tattheva bhagavato pādesu sirasā "
"nipatitvā bhagavato pādāni mukhena ca paricumbati pāṇīhi ca parisambāhati, "
"nāmañca sāveti:"
msgstr ""
"“The ascetic Gotama knows my mind!” He bowed with his head to the Buddha’s "
"feet, caressing them and covering them with kisses, and pronounced his name:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.3"
msgid "“mānatthaddhāhaṃ, bho gotama, mānatthaddhāhaṃ, bho gotamā”ti."
msgstr "“Master Gotama, I am Stuck-Up! I am Stuck-Up!”"

#. VAR: abbhutavittajātā → abbhutacittajātā (bj, km, pts1-2) | abbhūtacittajātā (s1-3) | acchariyabbhutacittajātā (mr)
msgctxt "sn7.15:3.4"
msgid "Atha kho sā parisā abbhutavittajātā ahosi:"
msgstr "Then that assembly was stunned:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.5"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, it’s amazing!"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.6"
msgid ""
"Ayañhi mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo neva mātaraṃ abhivādeti, na pitaraṃ abhivādeti, "
"na ācariyaṃ abhivādeti, na jeṭṭhabhātaraṃ abhivādeti;"
msgstr ""
"This brahmin Stuck-Up doesn’t bow to his mother or father, his teacher, or "
"his oldest brother."

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.7"
msgid "atha ca pana samaṇe gotame evarūpaṃ paramanipaccakāraṃ karotī”ti."
msgstr "Yet he shows such utmost devotion to the ascetic Gotama!”"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.8"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā mānatthaddhaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the brahmin Stuck-Up:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.9"
msgid "“alaṃ, brāhmaṇa, uṭṭhehi, sake āsane nisīda."
msgstr "“Enough, brahmin. Get up, and take your own seat."

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.10"
msgid "Yato te mayi cittaṃ pasannan”ti."
msgstr "For your mind has confidence in me.”"

msgctxt "sn7.15:3.11"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo sake āsane nisīditvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya "
"ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Stuck-Up took his seat and said to the Buddha:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.384"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.1"
msgid "“Kesu na mānaṃ kayirātha,"
msgstr "“Regarding whom should you not be conceited?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.2"
msgid "kesu cassa sagāravo;"
msgstr "Who should you respect?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.3"
msgid "Kyassa apacitā assu,"
msgstr "Who should you esteem?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:4.4"
msgid "kyassu sādhu supūjitā”ti."
msgstr "Who is it good to venerate properly?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.1"
msgid "“Mātari pitari cāpi,"
msgstr "“Your mother and father,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.2"
msgid "atho jeṭṭhamhi bhātari;"
msgstr "and also your oldest brother,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.3"
msgid "Ācariye catutthamhi,"
msgstr "with teacher as fourth."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.4"
msgid "tesu na mānaṃ kayirātha;"
msgstr "Regarding these you should not be conceited."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.5"
msgid "Tesu assa sagāravo,"
msgstr "They are who you should respect."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.6"
msgid "tyassa apacitā assu;"
msgstr "They are who you should esteem."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:5.7"
msgid "Tyassu sādhu supūjitā."
msgstr "And they’re who it’s good to venerate properly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.1"
msgid "Arahante sītībhūte,"
msgstr "And when you’ve humbled conceit, and aren’t stuck-up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.2"
msgid "katakicce anāsave;"
msgstr "show supreme reverence for"

# nihacca, though given in the dicts as “destroy, strike down”, is only used in contexts of conceit, or “bending the knee” to bow. It thus seems to have a more specific nuance.
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.3"
msgid "Nihacca mānaṃ athaddho,"
msgstr "the perfected ones, cooled,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.15:6.4"
msgid "te namasse anuttare”ti."
msgstr "their task complete, free of defilements.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.385"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.15:7.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, mānatthaddho brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Stuck-Up said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.15:7.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama …"

msgctxt "sn7.15:7.3"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"
